\begin_layout Standard
The learning step rely on an orchestral database composed of the scores (xml preferably, midi otherwise) and a recording. Each track is divided in (short) time frames (both score and recording). The two Siamese networks respectively receive in input a symbolic frame and its corresponding signal frame (or its FFT, or any other perceptually relevant transformation). The training is then divided in two steps 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
