\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The structure of the two networks have to be determined (recurrent nets or simple deep architectures ? Stacked memory ?), but the first step would rely on state of the art methods in automatic features extraction. A first remark for the second step is that it requires the two networks to have the same number of output units 
